_text = "I gasp awake.\n\nHave you had that dream where you are falling? I've only had it a couple times in my life, but the adrenaline of waking up is so severe it makes the world around you seem upside down.\n\nThis is how I feel waking up back in this cave.\n\nI'm no longer in that house, or swaying in that hammock. I'm back in the cold tunnel, surrounded by rock and debris.\n\nWhere I stand, I can see the tunnel beginning to end. The outside world is blinding. I feel like its my goal to get to the other side, to resolve everything I've thought about.\n\nBut I can see up ahead I have one last memory to comb through. There are some unpleasant memories to address first. Moments that I can't forget, even if I try to."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelTextRoom4_2, MemoryTunnelTextRoom4_2, false)
